gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 130, Mavericks 104
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Mavericks, 130-104. Jamal Murray led the way for the Nuggets with 22 points and four 3PM, while Aaron Gordon added 21 points, five rebounds and five assists in the victory. Luka Doncic tallied 38 points (6-12 3pt. FG), 11 rebounds and eight assists for the Mavericks in the losing effort. The Nuggets improve to 18-10 on the season, while the Mavericks fall to 16-10.
